{"tid":962420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲男手機手錶留天台墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-12-30T23:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T04:00:58.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cc5eef04b7180412e3f533d2219c2004fcdfb374","tid":962420,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T23:48:55.000Z","msg":"旺角亞皆老街36至38號龍飛大廈，凌晨4時許，一名20歲姓吳男子，從大廈高處墮下，重傷倒地昏迷不醒，奄奄一息，一輛衝鋒車巡經現場，警員立刻通報上鋒召救護車到場，惜傷者送院搶救後終告不治，地面留下死者波鞋。<br />\n<br />\n警員在大廈11樓天台，發現相信屬死者留下物品，包括有手機、充電器、手錶及啤酒罐，沒有撿獲遺書，初步沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=4gXlBYZ6EL0HpDvDIV0rjG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=35f7242e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181231/59088287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F59088287&d=4gXlBYZ6EL0HpDvDIV0rjG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7364f9b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F59088287&h=a5d89c99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181231/59088287</a>"},{"pid":"ebac40930870b1a524f9e353d365935bc4e26d07","tid":962420,"uid":228963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T23:54:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f71990652e957d21c28fde30f4184cf3da04fb2","tid":962420,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebac40930870b1a524f9e353d365935bc4e26d07","tid":962420,"uid":228963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T23:54:43.00